{"tid":1424114,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［跪地］求大家唔好再破壞深水埗警署","createTime":"2019-08-06T15:24:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T17:40:23.000Z","uid":128804,"like":48,"dislike":140,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"d8020554c4de64e464585cd83693eacebeff38bc","tid":1424114,"uid":128804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:24:12.000Z","msg":"大家唔好以為打爛塊玻璃仲有得換<br />\n<br />\n冇咗就係冇咗,之後要修復,就搵唔返一模一樣嘅返嚟<br />\n<br />\n依個警署係港英時代留落嚟嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n亦都係小弟發誓一生一世都要守護嘅香港歷史建築之一<br />\n<br />\n求吓大家,唔好令一個由69開始支持大家到嘅手足心碎<br />\n<br />\n頂多我應承大家,下一次發夢唔再企中排幫人沖水,再企前啲幫大家頂彈好唔好?<br />\n<br />\n唔好再破壞深水埗警署喇"},{"pid":"205e3c52c868f8ffc8c21370760b92cad66ac8f3","tid":1424114,"uid":128804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:24:26.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"2dda455ee24865af4eb3a157ad9db51b37a207a0","tid":1424114,"uid":128804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:24:40.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"8ece483ce52b52dd0a43f51076879d7d6fba0c21","tid":1424114,"uid":7818,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:24:46.000Z","msg":"香港都係港英時代留落嚟嘅嘢"},{"pid":"d8cf00c4932af8cb7f0c71c7c4c82acb119c8643","tid":1424114,"uid":128804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:24:52.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"f070a3fc64d661b0d4f48c7393f9c8048beab259","tid":1424114,"uid":67574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:24:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"47b1462b4a00a20801de52997003cbf3a114850f","tid":1424114,"uid":128804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:25:03.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"de169f4b8a9153f59f6e217387078c96f583279b","tid":1424114,"uid":78349,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8ece483ce52b52dd0a43f51076879d7d6fba0c21","tid":1424114,"uid":7818,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:24:46.000Z","msg":"香港都係港英時代留落嚟嘅嘢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-0